課程概述 Course Description
       成功大學建築系五年制學士班之教育目標在培養學生建築創意設計能力，以空間的美感與創造為主，人文歷史與環境關懷為輔，期能有符應社會職能需求的人文素養，成為建築、空間與環境設計專業人才。The five-year Bachelor of Architecture program prepares students to become practitioners in interior, building, urban and environmental designs. The program focuses on the fundamental knowledge bases a multidisciplinary career dealing with the built envir    

課程學習目標 Course Objectives    
	    成功大學建築系五年制學士班之教育目標在培養學生建築創意設計能力，以空間的美感與創造為主，人文歷史與環境關懷為輔，期能有符應社會職能需求的人文素養，成為建築、空間與環境設計專業人才。
The five-year Bachelor of Architecture program prepares students to become practitioners in interior, building, urban and environmental designs. The program focuses on the fundamental knowledge bases a multidisciplinary career dealing with the built environment, which involves artistic creativity, analytical reasoning, technical capability, social consciousness, and historical perspective.    

